Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:10.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你们在干嘛？莫妮卡逼我们看《老黄狗》（又译《父亲离家时》）{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-What you guys doing? -Monica's making us watch Old Yeller.{\r}
