Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:50.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}他从来不会乱指乱戳 口气永远芳香自然{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}He keeps his fingers to himself,and he's always minty fresh.{\r}
