Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对呀，我跟我外婆讲了 那个“老黄狗”那件事…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I talked to my grandma about the Old Yeller incident...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:28.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}…她说我妈总是不让我们看 那种悲伤电影的结局…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...and she said my mom used to not show us the ends of sad movies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}…好让我们不用痛苦伤心{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...to shield us from the pain and sadness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:34.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你们知道的，是在她自杀之前{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You know,before she killed herself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:40.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}他人呢？理查呢？ 你们甩了他吗？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Where's Richard? Did you ditch him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:43.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对，在抢了他的午餐钱还有拉了他内裤（国外小孩的恶作剧）之后{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}After we stole his lunch money and gave him a wedgie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:47.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你这人怎么搞的？他在停车{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}What's the matter? He's parking the car.{\r}
