Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}他连多少都没看，就像这样{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You never even saw the money.{\r}
