Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}钱德留那胡子 像不像西维亚姑妈？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}With that mustache,he reminds me of Aunt Sylvia.{\r}
