Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}只是他空闲的时间不多 我不知道，我到底该怎么办？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}He just doesn't have much free time. What do I do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:08.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}有关系吗？你始终都会死 或离婚，或枪杀你的宠物{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Does it matter? You'll just die or divorce or blow your pet's head off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我也是{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Me too!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:17.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}瑞秋，我有个问题 理查又跟他们做计划了…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Rachel,I got a question. Richard made plans again with the guys{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对，罗斯刚计划了整个世纪{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Ross made plans for the century.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:23.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我想我要回房去看时尚杂志了 或许会读到什么有用的{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm gonna go read Cosmo. Maybe there's something helpful in it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:28.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}不然至少可以学会 怎样用圣诞树剩下的蜡烛除毛{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}If not,I can learn how to do a bikini wax with leftover Christmas candles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你刚刚是怎么回事？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}What happened back there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}不知道，你告诉我吧{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't know. You tell me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:38.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我刚刚还像抱足球一样抱着班 接下来我就有两个孩子…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}One minute I'm holding Ben,then I've got two kids...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:41.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}…住在斯卡斯代尔，抱怨着税太高{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}... I'm living in Scarsdale complaining about taxes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}那抱歉，我就是爱想些事情{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Well,I'm sorry. I think about stuff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:48.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我是说，工作的时候 一边弄骨头就会一边乱想嘛{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You're at work,you're assembling bones,your mind wanders.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你计划了我们往后二十年生活 我们才在一起六周{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You've planned out the next 20 years. We've dated for six weeks!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你从不想未来的事吗？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You never think about our future?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:57.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}想，但我想的是 我们明晚住谁那边好…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I think about whose apartment we'll sleep at tomorrow...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}…下个礼拜六晚上 我们去哪里吃晚饭{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...and where we'll have dinner next Saturday!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我不会去想 我们的孩子会叫什么名字{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I do not think about our children's names!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你知道我们的孩子会叫什么名字对吧？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You know what our children's names will be?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:12.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}不…我…我是说我看到一本书 里头有个女孩叫艾蜜莉{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}No,I mean,you know. I read a book,and there was a girl named Emily.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我觉得…我觉得还不错{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}And I thought that might be good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}哪一本书？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}What book?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}“儿童命名大全”{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}The Big Book of Children's Names.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你听着{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Okay,listen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们在一起很棒{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}What we have is amazing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:29.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}但我不要别人为我决定好一切{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}But I do not want everything decided for me!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我那样过一辈子了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I spent my whole life like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我跟贝瑞就是那样 那是我离开的原因之一{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}It's what I had with Barry. That's a reason I left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我喜欢有未知{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I like not knowing right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:40.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}如果那样吓着了你，那很抱歉 但若你要跟我在一起就接受吧{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Sorry if that scares you,but if you wanna be with me,deal with that!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}好，很好 谢谢{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Okay,fine! -Thank you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}还没完呢 那我不知道{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-We're not done! -I didn't know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:49.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}跟你在一起的人 不会停止去计划他跟你的未来{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You're with a guy who won't stop planning his future with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}因为他知道我们最后会在一起{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}He knows we'll end up together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:54.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}如果你害怕了，很不幸 因为你必须学会接受{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}If that scares you,tough! You'll have to deal with that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}很好，我会的 好，因为我爱你{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-I will! -Good,because I love you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}是吗？我也爱你{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Oh,yeah? I love you too!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们第一次互相说我爱你 没错{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-That's the first time we've said that! -Yes,it is!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}那我就要亲你了 最好是这样{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-I'm gonna kiss you! -You better!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}谢谢你给我的建议{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Thanks for the great movie tip.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你喜欢吗？ 喜欢{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Did you like it? -Oh,yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我不知道我是该在乔治毁了事业之后…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I don't know if I was happier when George Bailey destroyed the business...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:23.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}…还是在唐娜哭或是在药剂师害他耳朵流血时会比较快乐{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...or Donna Reed cried or when the pharmacist made his ear bleed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:27.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}好吧，我选耳朵流血 你不觉得结局很好吗？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'll give you the ear thing,but wasn't the ending wonderful?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}结局我根本就没看 我太沮丧了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I didn't watch it. I was too depressed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}剧情越来越叫人家失望 这片子应该叫：{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}It kept getting worse! It should've been called:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:37.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}“人生真烂 就在你觉得无法更烂时，它更烂”{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}"It's a Sucky Life,And Just When You Think It Can't Suck Anymore,It Does!"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}踢球，守住！{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}IKick,save! And...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}…接住了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}...denied!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:47.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}但他抢回来，传到中间 然后准备踢，碰…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}He gets it back. Pass to the middle,lines it up....{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:48.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}太棒了！{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:52.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}那球还可以踢得更漂亮吗？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Could that shot be any prettier?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:54.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}老兄，你真厉害{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Man,you are incredible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们大学时也有这玩意儿{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}We had a table in college.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我不晓得 1800年也有桌上足球{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Really? I didn't know they had foosball in the 1800s.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对了，你的胡子不错 青春期一到就会茂盛起来{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Nice mustache. At puberty,that thing will really kick in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:12.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我也不想太像福劳伦斯汉德森（女演员） 但晚餐做好了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Not to sound too Florence Henderson,but dinner's on the table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}再得一分{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}One more point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}得分{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Score!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}可以走了吗？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Now can we go?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}看吧，所以我们才不让她玩{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}That's why we don't let her play.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}一切都还好吧？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Is everything all right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:32.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}听我说，别跟他生气 是我们的错{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Don't be mad at him. It's our fault.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我们占了他太多时间了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm sorry we've been hogging his time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:37.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}是呀，跟他真的是很棒{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}He's just really great to hang out with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}这个嘛… 不…说真的{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Well.... -No,seriously.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:42.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我跟钱德刚才还在说 他比我们的爸爸酷多了{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}We just talked about this. He is so much cooler than our dads.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:48.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我是说我们爸爸是还好啦 可是理查好…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}Our dads are okay and all,but Richard is just{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你踢我干什么？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}What are you kicking me for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}我正在讲话，你…{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}I'm trying to talk here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}你们觉得我像父辈的？{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}You guys see me as a dad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn幼圆\fs16\bord1\3c&HFF8000&}对呀 不{\r}\N{\fnTahoma\fs14\bord1\1c&H00FFFF&}-Oh,yeah! -No!{\r}
